author: mrglavas
msg: Once the DOMParser has completed building the DOM drop all internal references
to the completed Document object. If the application is pooling parsers this
will allow the garbage collector to reclaim the Document and all of its nodes
if the application no longer has any references to it.

author: pdodds
msg: Implemented new feature that allows you to specify a jbiServicesFile (default location src/main/resources/jbi-services.xml) that can be used to inject the services definition into the jbi.xml for a service unit - this can also be used to override the services generated by a ServiceUnitAnalyzer
